name: Experiment Or Die #30
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. You never know how your life might veer depending on what you might encounter day to day. I lived in NY, moved to Atlanta for Portfolio School in 2004 and earned an internship BACK in NYC and while I was there was dragged to a show at the Kidrobot store. All of those series of events led me to designer toys and here I am 17 years later. IG: Nikejerk
